# cc-unlock line-ending policy
# 保证跨平台 checkout 时脚本换行正确，避免 Windows 的 autocrlf 把 bash 脚本转成 CRLF 而崩溃。

# Shell scripts and macOS launchers must always be LF (CRLF breaks bash/zsh)
*.sh        text eol=lf
*.command   text eol=lf

# Windows batch files must always be CRLF
*.bat       text eol=crlf

# .ps1 is intentionally left to the default (autocrlf): deploy.ps1 carries a UTF-8 BOM
# and is Windows-only, so its line endings never cross platforms. PowerShell reads any EOL.
